com.petpet.c3po.analysis
Class DistributionRepresentativeGenerator

java.lang.Object
  com.petpet.c3po.analysis.RepresentativeGenerator
      com.petpet.c3po.analysis.DistributionRepresentativeGenerator

public class DistributionRepresentativeGenerator
extends RepresentativeGenerator

This class generates a sample set based on a distribution coverage strategy. It calculates the distributions of the values of each of the given properties and tries to find a sample set that has similar distribution for the given values. Note that giving many properties will most certainly result in an empty set. Note that giving exclusive properties (e.g. pagecount and audio_dataencoding) will always result in an empty set. Note that this version of the strategy does not detect outliers.

Author:
Petar Petrov
